We teamed up to give one lucky winner their own picnic essentials!!

Here’s what you’ll win! 💗
✨A box of @trufru goodies (value of $100+)
✨A $200 gift card from @jessakae
✨Chatham Rev Electric Beach Cruiser valued at $1,400

HOW TO ENTER:
1️⃣Like & save this post
2️⃣Follow both @jessakae and @trufru
3️⃣Tag your friends in the comments! (The more tags, the more entries 😝)

The giveaway ends 7/13 at 11:59 pm MT and winners will be announced Thursday, July 14 🤍 US only! The winners comment will be pinned and DM’d from @trufru or @jessakae 💗

!!! LOS ANGELES COSTCO !!! 

Piña Colada trü frü is available in @costco now!!! We’re jumping with excitement. 🤩 So naturally, we are going to do a giveaway. One lucky winner will get a $200 Costco gift card and a box of trü frü! 🍍 

Here is how to enter:
1. Follow us @trufru
2. Like this post
3. Tag a friend (each tag must be its own comment + multiple tags are allowed)

This giveaway will run until June 29th. The winner will be announced in our stories, pinned comment below, and dm'd FROM THIS ACCOUNT! Beware of scammers, this is our only account!! US only.

Good Luck everyone! Woo hoo!!

latestPosts.caption:
We’ve seen a lot of brides walk down the aisle... but never in the freezer section. @trufru teamed up with @litiagarr to prove that not every aisle ends in “I do.”⁠
⁠
Some lead straight to the good stuff — aka the freezer, where Trü Frü awaits. 🍓🍌🍫⁠
⁠
So if you’re headed down the aisle this summer, make sure the freezer aisle is one of them. ⁠
⁠
👉🏼 Which Trü Frü flavor would you say “I do” to first?⁠
⁠
